<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>衡點 Dash 安裝教學</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --green: #7ac19a;
            --green-dark: #5f846f;
            --pink: #f2ac98;
            --yellow: #ffe08b;
            --blue: #9fcccc;
            --danger: #e05252;
            --bg: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2ede6 0%, #daedec 30%, #faece8 60%, #fcf4e3 100%);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--bg);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #2d3436;
            padding: 0 0 60px 0;
        }

        /* ── Header ── */
        .guide-header {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            padding: 24px 20px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .guide-header img {
            width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .guide-header h1 {
            font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-dark);
        }
        .guide-header p {
            font-size: 13px; color: #888; margin-top: 4px;
        }

        /* ── Phase Card ── */
        .phase {
            margin: 20px 16px 0;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .phase-header {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
            padding: 16px 18px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        }
        .phase-number {
            width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .phase-number.p1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6BCB77, #4AA96C); }
        .phase-number.p2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4D96FF, #3B7DD8); }
        .phase-header-text h2 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #2d3436; }
        .phase-header-text p { font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 2px; }

        /* ── Step ── */
        .step-list { padding: 4px 0 8px; }

        .step {
            display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step + .step {
            border-top: 1px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .step-icon {
            width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0;
            background: rgba(122,193,154,0.12);
        }
        .step-icon.safari { background: rgba(77,150,255,0.1); }
        .step-icon.share { background: rgba(77,150,255,0.1); }
        .step-icon.add { background: rgba(255,224,139,0.3); }
        .step-icon.login { background: rgba(242,172,152,0.2); }
        .step-icon.warn { background: rgba(224,82,82,0.1); }
        .step-icon.done { background: rgba(122,193,154,0.15); }
        .step-icon.liff { background: rgba(6,199,85,0.1); }
        .step-icon.form { background: rgba(159,204,204,0.2); }

        .step-content { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
        .step-title {
            font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #2d3436;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .step-desc {
            font-size: 12.5px; color: #777; margin-top: 4px; line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ── Warning Box ── */
        .warning-box {
            margin: 10px 18px 8px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            background: rgba(224,82,82,0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(224,82,82,0.15);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
        }
        .warning-box .warn-icon {
            font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .warning-box .warn-text {
            font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--danger); line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 500;
        }
        .warning-box .warn-text strong {
            color: #c0392b; font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* ── Tip Box ── */
        .tip-box {
            margin: 10px 18px 8px;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            background: rgba(122,193,154,0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(122,193,154,0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
        }
        .tip-box .tip-icon {
            font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .tip-box .tip-text {
            font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--green-dark); line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ── Visual Demo Box ── */
        .demo-box {
            margin: 10px 18px 8px;
            padding: 14px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            border-radius: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .demo-box .demo-label {
            font-size: 11px; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .demo-row {
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .demo-choice {
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        .demo-choice.correct {
            background: rgba(122,193,154,0.12);
            border-color: var(--green);
            color: var(--green-dark);
        }
        .demo-choice.wrong {
            background: rgba(224,82,82,0.06);
            border-color: rgba(224,82,82,0.3);
            color: #999;
            text-decoration: line-through;
        }
        .demo-arrow {
            font-size: 16px; color: #ccc;
        }

        /* ── CTA Button ── */
        .cta-section {
            margin: 24px 16px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-btn {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: var(--green-dark);
            color: #fff;
            border: none; border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(95,132,111,0.3);
            transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
        }
        .cta-btn:active {
            transform: scale(0.97);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(95,132,111,0.2);
        }
        .cta-btn + .cta-btn {
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        .cta-btn.secondary {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            color: var(--green-dark);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(95,132,111,0.2);
        }

        .cta-note {
            font-size: 11px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 12px;
        }

        /* ── Footer ── */
        .guide-footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 11px; color: #bbb;
        }

        /* ── Progress Connector ── */
        .phase-connector {
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
        }
        .phase-connector .arrow {
            font-size: 24px; color: #ccc;
        }

        /* ── Share Icon inline SVG ── */
        .inline-share-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 16px; height: 16px;
            vertical-align: -2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="guide-header">
        <img src="icon-192.png" alt="衡點 Dash">
        <h1>衡點 Dash 安裝教學</h1>
        <p>3 分鐘完成設定，之後一鍵開啟</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- Phase 1: 首次綁定 -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="phase">
        <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-number p1">1</div>
            <div class="phase-header-text">
                <h2>首次身份綁定</h2>
                <p>只需做一次，綁定你的 LINE 帳號</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-list">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon liff">💬</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <div class="step-title">點選下方綁定連結</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">會自動在 LINE 中開啟綁定頁面</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon form">📋</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <div class="step-title">填寫資料並送出</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">依照頁面指示完成資料填寫後，按下送出即可</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon done">✅</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <div class="step-title">綁定完成</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">看到成功提示後即完成，可關閉此頁面</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-box">
            <div class="tip-icon">💡</div>
            <div class="tip-text">此步驟只需做一次。綁定後系統即可辨識你的身份。</div>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 12px 18px 16px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://liff.line.me/2007947083-YCFwz7Uk" class="cta-btn" style="display:inline-flex;">
                <span>💬</span> 開始綁定
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Connector -->
    <div class="phase-connector">
        <div class="arrow">⬇️</div>
    </div>

    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <!-- Phase 2: 安裝 PWA -->
    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="phase">
        <div class="phase-header">
            <div class="phase-number p2">2</div>
            <div class="phase-header-text">
                <h2>安裝到手機桌面</h2>
                <p>iPhone 使用 Safari 操作</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-list">
            <!-- Step 2-1 -->
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon safari">🧭</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <div class="step-title">用 Safari 開啟下方連結</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">
                        請務必使用 <strong>Safari</strong> 瀏覽器開啟<br>
                        <span style="color:#4D96FF;font-size:11.5px;word-break:break-all;">https://oxencust.github.io/admin-portal/</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2-2 -->
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon share">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4D96FF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 3v12"/><path d="M8 7l4-4 4 4"/><rect x="4" y="13" width="16" height="8" rx="2"/>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <div class="step-title">點擊 Safari 底部的「分享」按鈕</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">就是底部工具列中間的 <svg class="inline-share-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4D96FF" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3v12"/><path d="M8 7l4-4 4 4"/><rect x="4" y="13" width="16" height="8" rx="2"/></svg> 方框加箭頭的圖示</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2-3 -->
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon add">➕</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <div class="step-title">選擇「加入主畫面」</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">在分享選單中往下滑，找到「加入主畫面」後點擊，再按右上角「新增」</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2-4 -->
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon login">🔑</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <div class="step-title">從桌面開啟，選擇「輸入帳號密碼」</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">首次開啟 App 會看到 LINE 登入畫面，出現兩個選項時，請選擇<strong>「輸入帳號密碼」</strong>登入</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Warning: Don't use LINE app login -->
        <div class="warning-box">
            <div class="warn-icon">⚠️</div>
            <div class="warn-text">
                <strong>請勿選擇「使用 LINE 應用程式登入」</strong><br>
                選了會跳到 LINE App 導致無法正常返回，造成畫面不斷重複載入。請一定要選「輸入帳號密碼」手動輸入 LINE 的 Email 和密碼。
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Visual: correct vs wrong choice -->
        <div class="demo-box">
            <div class="demo-label">登入畫面選擇</div>
            <div class="demo-row">
                <div class="demo-choice wrong">❌ 使用LINE應用程式登入</div>
                <div class="demo-choice correct">✅ 輸入帳號密碼</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2-5 -->
        <div class="step-list" style="padding-top:0;">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-icon done">🎉</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                    <div class="step-title">完成！之後直接從桌面開啟即可</div>
                    <div class="step-desc">登入一次後系統會記住你的身份，之後都不用重新登入</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-box">
            <div class="tip-icon">💡</div>
            <div class="tip-text">
                如果你還沒設定 LINE 的 Email 和密碼：<br>
                打開 LINE → 設定 ⚙️ → 我的帳號 → Email / 密碼<br>
                先設定好再回來操作即可。
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 12px 18px 16px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://oxencust.github.io/admin-portal/" class="cta-btn secondary">
                <span>🧭</span> 用 Safari 開啟衡點 Dash
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="guide-footer">
        衡點健康管理 &copy; 2026<br>
        有問題請聯繫管理員
    </div>

</body>
</html>
